### Transfers — options, execution, PIN & eligibility rules. Self-contained: run top to bottom.
### Transaction PIN (seeded): 123456.

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "demo",
  "password": "password123"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("token", response.body.accessToken);
%}

### Source account
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

> {%
    client.global.set("accountId", response.body[0].id);
%}

### Eligible methods for a small amount → BI_FAST + ONLINE
GET {{baseUrl}}/transfers/options?amount=15000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Large amount → RTGS only appears Mon–Fri 08:00–15:00 WIB
GET {{baseUrl}}/transfers/options?amount=150000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Execute a BI-FAST transfer (fee Rp2.500 is added to the debit)
POST {{baseUrl}}/transfers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sourceAccountId": "{{accountId}}",
  "destBankCode": "MANDIRI",
  "destAccountNumber": "9988776655",
  "destAccountName": "SITI AMINAH",
  "amount": 50000,
  "method": "BI_FAST",
  "note": "test via http client",
  "pin": "123456"
}

### Wrong PIN → 400 INVALID_PIN, nothing debited
POST {{baseUrl}}/transfers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sourceAccountId": "{{accountId}}",
  "destBankCode": "MANDIRI",
  "destAccountNumber": "9988776655",
  "destAccountName": "SITI AMINAH",
  "amount": 50000,
  "method": "BI_FAST",
  "pin": "000000"
}

### Ineligible method → 400 METHOD_NOT_ELIGIBLE (15.000 is below the RTGS minimum)
POST {{baseUrl}}/transfers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sourceAccountId": "{{accountId}}",
  "destBankCode": "MANDIRI",
  "destAccountNumber": "9988776655",
  "destAccountName": "SITI AMINAH",
  "amount": 15000,
  "method": "RTGS",
  "pin": "123456"
}

### Amount above balance → 400 INSUFFICIENT_BALANCE
POST {{baseUrl}}/transfers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sourceAccountId": "{{accountId}}",
  "destBankCode": "MANDIRI",
  "destAccountNumber": "9988776655",
  "destAccountName": "SITI AMINAH",
  "amount": 200000000,
  "method": "BI_FAST",
  "pin": "123456"
}
